    "type": "message",
    "text": "I just listened this podcast <https://reactpodcast.com/26>. Might be boring the beginning for people not interested in design or frontend development.\nBut the second half has interesting ideas:\n- How to write code that survives technology trends. Not siloing it would be a great way to start, like writing CSS in JS could be a problem later.\n- Great hearing the perspective of a designer on programming.",
