    "attachments": [
      {
        "service_name": "React Podcast",
        "title": "26: Chill Out and Listen with Brad Frost | React Podcast",
        "title_link": "https://reactpodcast.com/26",
        "text": "Brad Frost is the author of Atomic Design, renowned speaker, and consulting designer. Chantastic asks him about his recent experience learning React and the difficulty he found entering the realm of React. They talk about team communication, developing portable solutions, organizational therapy through design, and creating a virtuous cycle between product, design, development, and systems creating. They address the challenges of learning UI design in an industry being consumed by JavaScript, the importance of listening and the value of finding nuance in communication.",
